title: US unemployment filings surge, reaches two-year high amid coronavirus outbreak
description: The coronavirus crisis stands to do damage to the U.S. economy and job market with the potential to send the U.S. unemployment rate much higher; Fox Business correspondent Susan Li reports.

title: Automakers offer to produce medical supplies to fight coronavirus
description: From Ford to General Motors to Tesla, automakers offer to jump start production of ventilators and other desperately needed medical equipment; senior correspondent Claudia Cowan reports from Fremont, California.
